text: Hammarby IF BF is a bandy club in Stockholm in Sweden. Established in 1905, the club won the Swedish national men's bandy championship in the years of 2010 and 2013. ==References== ==Other websites== *Hammarby IF BF Category:1905 establishments in Europe Category:Bandy clubs in Sweden Category:1900s establishments in Sweden
